init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: All of the Dads, everywhere, collectively lose their minds.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As the Dads try to figure out how they are ranked, more and more dads in the world realize their ranking isn't what they were

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Eventually, a high ranking Dad realizes that the rankings are based on the number of kids that each dad has.
